{"id":605416,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/【立此存照】新年敏感热点：春晚无聊、魔术托儿/","date":"2019-02-06T11:39:10Z","modified":"2019-02-06T11:39:10Z","title":"【立此存照】新年敏感热点：春晚无聊、魔术托儿、新兴医药","content":"<p>近日，有关春节联欢晚会的相关吐槽遭到了网络审查。大年三十当天新浪微博上陆续屏蔽了“春晚无聊”、“春晚吐槽”等词，甚至有微博网友频发相关内容遭遇封号。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyjQ8fJU8AAoJyi.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-605418\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyjQ8fJU8AAoJyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"207\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyjQ8fJU8AAoJyi.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyjQ8fJU8AAoJyi-300x124.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyjQ8fJU8AAoJyi-768x318.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/Dyry71WX0AIcgm3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-605419\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/Dyry71WX0AIcgm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"218\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/Dyry71WX0AIcgm3.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/Dyry71WX0AIcgm3-300x131.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/Dyry71WX0AIcgm3-768x335.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>除此之外，春晚刘谦的魔术表演助手当众换壶以全场观众为托的视频意外流出，引不少网民愤怒，在初一短时间成为热门。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Seen on WeChat: how the Taiwanese magician Lu “Louis” Liu 刘谦 performed his “Jesus” trick of transforming water into wine during the CCTV New Year Gala (spoiler: someone is changing his pot): <a href=\"https://t.co/g0HcN7tRIn\">pic.twitter.com/g0HcN7tRIn</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Nathanel Amar 馬泰然 (@nathanelamarHK) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanelamarHK/status/1093027499317985280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 6, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">所有的在场观众都是你的托，无一例外，却还在信誓旦旦，用人格、生命、名誉来担保，无耻得像某组织一样！ <a href=\"https://t.co/iQ9gtBgOcK\">pic.twitter.com/iQ9gtBgOcK</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 秀才江湖 (@xiucai1911) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/xiucai1911/status/1092763826649325569?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 5, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>然而有网友发现，已有视频平台在审查相关视频，禁止该视频的上传，所列原因为：接上级通知，稿件不予通过。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-605420\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA-300x148.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA-768x379.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DysGQ0pU8AAnedA-1024x505.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>春节期间所发生的又一起重大的疫苗安全事件“上海新兴血液制品艾滋抗体阳性”，正在被有关部门压制网络热度，有知乎网友反映，自己的有关提问不但被强制解散，账号还遭封禁一天。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyprtcnWsAQSExe.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-605421\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyprtcnWsAQSExe.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyprtcnWsAQSExe.jpg 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyprtcnWsAQSExe-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/DyprtcnWsAQSExe-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[37893,9249,25709,37894,14070,37890,37896,37895]}